column5: Question, any body know of a place between the border crossing at Roseau and Winnipeg where you can buy frogs? or Goldeye? going to Lockport Manitoaba for cats at the Red River and sometimes we have trouble catching our goldeyes there because of river conditions, thtanks for any input
